findings.title: Deployer can mint any new tokens after deployment
findings.description: The deployer has the ability to mint new tokens even after the initial deployment.

findings.title: Deployer can burn or lock user funds
findings.description: The deployer does not have the capability to burn or lock user funds.

findings.title: Deployer can pause contract
findings.description: The deployer has the capability to pause the contract.

findings.title: Deployer can set max transaction limit
findings.description: The deployer has the ability to set a maximum transaction limit, which could potentially lead to unintended consequences or restrictions on transactions.
